channel.title: Error while running StabbingScape source
channel.description:
if your familiar with this error and know how to solve it please help!@ I click compile and i get: compiling.... Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Compiling finished press any key to continue.
people say it doesn't matter when it says that.
then i hit run and this comes up:
- StabbingScape Online -
then i hit run server and this comes up:
Can't start your port on 43594, could be on already.
what does it mean???

item.title: Error while running StabbingScape source
item.dc:creator: @boysonwheelz boysonwheelz
item.description:
@boysonwheelz wrote:

do u use utorrent cause if so thats a common error just open and change to random port, close run, then open run back up and it should work then change the random port in ur utorrent to 43594 then close run then reopen and it will work.
